<span id="freeTextContainer1152324439199373155">I really enjoyed this book. It&apos;s written in a style which makes it a pleasure to read. The main characters are either people you can empathise with or hate. <br/>A cop&apos;s father was killed by a serial killer called The Phantom and she is determined to bring the killer to justice. The story of Ben is a rather harrowing one but I won&apos;t give too much away as I wouldn&apos;t want to spoil the story for future readers</span>
